snippet.title: Legends BMX 🚲 Extreme sports videogame | Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3291690/Legends_BMX/
Wishlist on PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/concept/10013002/

Pure Flow and Adrenaline! LEGENDS BMX is an energetic and exhilarating #videogame made for #extremesports and #sports enthusiasts that will be available on Steam, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series and Nintendo Switch! Ride your BMX through a variety of parks and scenarios designed to let you pull off incredible tricks.

More news on the launch on Xbox Series and Nintendo Switch coming very soon!

#bmx #bmxlife #extremesports
